<TrustPageLayout
  title="Partnerships and affiliates — DubaiPoints"
  description="How DubaiPoints handles affiliate links, brand partnerships and sponsored content. Independence is non-negotiable; the financial firewall is in writing."
  eyebrow="Partnerships"
  heading="Where the money does and doesn't come from."
  deck="If we ever earn affiliate commission on a card application — we don't yet — every link is marked with an asterisk and a footnote linking here. This page is the firewall, and it stays that way."
